column3:
やったコロォ～
この調子でルーダニアを追い詰めるコロォ～
column4:
We did it, goro! If we can keep this up,
we should be able to cornerRudania.

column3: やったぁ～また当たったコロォ～

ダルケルの護りがあれば全く痛くないコロ！
流石 ご先祖様コロ！
この調子で弱らせれば中に入れるかもね
さぁ あと一息コロ！
column4:
And thanks toDaruk's Protection,
that didn't hurt me one bit, goro!
My ancestor came through for me!
If we keep weakening it like this,
we should be able to get inside.
Don't let up, brother!
